{
  "texts": [
    "Because of longer waves, in the two high wind speed cases of 14.82 and 16.59 m s -1, there exist a number of waves for which the entire wavelength of the wave cannot be captured in the PIV field of view.",
    "We observed that the ML model performs best for the cases where at least one wavelength has been captured.",
    "Another contributor to this increased error might be the increase in the signal-to-noise ratio of the PIV measurements with wind speed.",
    "The unseen cases of W1-02 and W1-14 are discussed in § 3.4.",
    "The relative errors reported in table 2 provide an average measure over the entire dataset."
  ]
}